= Description
  A small Ruby library for generating Azure Shared Access Signature (SAS) tokens.

= Synopsis
  require 'azure/sastoken' 

  token = SasToken.new('http://yourexamplenamespace', 'some-policy', 'xxxyyyzzz')

  p token

= Acknowledgements
  I heavily borrowed code from the azure-push library from Christian S.

= Author
  Daniel Berger
